{
  "texts": [
    "[how] Presentation §A.2.3: Determined by how insights extracted by the interpretability method are presented to the stakeholder.",
    "This includes scores, such as importance scores or metrics, and visualization, such as heatmaps and graphs.",
    "Other explanations present similar or contrastive examples to stakeholders or communicate insights through texts written in natural language.",
    "[how] Causal-based §A.2.4: Providing faithful explanations might involve incorporating techniques from the causality literature.",
    "This property determines whether the method is causal-based or not."
  ]
}